      <description>&lt;div style=&#34;position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 12px 0; margin: 0 0 24px 0; display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;#check-coverage&#34; style=&#34;padding: 6px 14px; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #475569; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;&#34;&gt;Check Coverage&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;#prior-auth&#34; style=&#34;padding: 6px 14px; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #475569; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;&#34;&gt;Prior Authorization&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;#qualifying-conditions&#34; style=&#34;padding: 6px 14px; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #475569; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;&#34;&gt;Qualifying Conditions&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;#denied&#34; style=&#34;padding: 6px 14px; background: #fef2f2; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #dc2626; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;&#34;&gt;If Denied&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;#alternatives&#34; style=&#34;padding: 6px 14px; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #475569; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;&#34;&gt;Alternatives&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%); border: 2px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 style=&#34;margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #92400e;&#34;&gt;⚡ The Reality Check&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p style=&#34;margin: 0; color: #78350f; line-height: 1.6;&#34;&gt;Most insurance plans don&#39;t cover Zepbound for weight loss. I tried to get it covered — my insurance excluded weight loss medications entirely, and finding doctors willing to write prior authorizations was a hassle. I ended up going self-pay. This guide covers everything I learned, including what to do if you hit the same wall.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
